### API Gateway Test Requests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@apiSlug = httpbin
@apiKey = YOUR_API_KEY_HERE

### 1. Test GET Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/proxy/{{apiSlug}}/get
X-MF-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### 2. Test POST Request with JSON
POST {{baseUrl}}/proxy/{{apiSlug}}/post
X-MF-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Hello from MeterFlow Gateway",
    "test": true
}

### 3. Test Rate Limiting (Run this multiple times)
GET {{baseUrl}}/proxy/{{apiSlug}}/get
X-MF-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### 4. Test Invalid Slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/proxy/invalid-slug/get
X-MF-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### 5. Test Missing API Key
GET {{baseUrl}}/proxy/{{apiSlug}}/get

### 6. Test Invalid API Key
GET {{baseUrl}}/proxy/{{apiSlug}}/get
X-MF-API-Key: invalid_key
